Your document is fine as both HTML and XHTML, the only thing that is kind of discouraged in the HTML serialization is self-cloding tags ending in /&gt; even though they are fully valid (and I use them too in HTML for my own reasons). The rest will probably never become non-conforming.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=377">lyosha</a> — Wed Mar 11, 2009 10:11 pm</p><hr />
